<div class="call-to-action">
<h3 id="support-for-people-affected-by-the-grenfell-tower-tragedy">Support for people affected by the Grenfell Tower tragedy</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/grenfell-tower-fire-june-2017-support-for-people-affected">Information about the support available for people affected by the Grenfell tragedy can be found here.</a></p>

<h3 id="soil-and-environmental-checks">Soil and environmental checks</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/soil-and-environmental-checks">See information on soil and environmental checks.</a></p>

<h3 id="building-safety-programme">Building Safety Programme</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/building-safety-programme">Find out more and receive updates on the Building Safety Programme, established by the government to identify buildings of concern through a comprehensive checking and testing process.</a></p>

<h3 id="enquiries-about-the-fire-safety-of-your-building">Enquiries about the fire safety of your building</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/fire-safety-of-your-building-advice-for-tenants-and-residents">Information about what you can do if you have concerns regarding the safety of your building.</a></p>
