  <h3 class="group-title" id="public-inquiry">Public Inquiry</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Governmentâ€™s Position Statement describes the actions the department has taken since the Grenfell Tower fire to make buildings safer.</p>

<p>To view the exhibits, which are referenced in the statement, please visit the <a rel="external" href="https://www.grenfelltowerinquiry.org.uk/evidence/mhclg-position-statement-building-safety-timeline">Grenfell Tower Inquiryâ€™s website</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>


  <div data-module="track-click">
